@page "/corporate"

<PageTitle>Corporate Fleet Training</PageTitle>

<Transition>
<div class="course-bg corporate"></div>
<div class="course-page corporate">

  <section class="intro reveal">
    <h1>Corporate Fleet Training – Build a Safer and Smarter Fleet</h1>
    <p>
      Our <b>Corporate Fleet Training Program</b> is designed for companies that operate commercial vehicles
      and want to improve safety, compliance, and driver performance.  
      Whether you manage <b>5 trucks or 500</b>, we offer flexible, MTO-compliant training to fit your business goals.
    </p>
    <p>
      We help fleets reduce accident rates, lower insurance costs, and keep their drivers professionally certified and confident on the road.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="overview reveal">
    <h2>Program Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Each program is tailored to your company’s operations — from entry-level onboarding to advanced defensive driving and safety refreshers.
      Training is conducted on-site, at your yard, or at our Vaughan facility using your vehicles or ours.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Customized corporate training plans</li>
      <li>Defensive driving and incident prevention</li>
      <li>Pre-trip inspections and vehicle maintenance awareness</li>
      <li>Regulatory compliance (MTO, CVOR, DOT)</li>
      <li>Fuel-efficient and eco-driving techniques</li>
      <li>Post-collision evaluation and driver retraining</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="training reveal">
    <h2>Training Modules</h2>
    <div class="facts">
      <div><b>Defensive Driving:</b> hazard perception, following distance, weather adjustments</div>
      <div><b>Compliance &amp; Documentation:</b> HOS, daily logs, CVOR, and carrier audits</div>
      <div><b>Fleet Safety:</b> in-yard protocols, PPE, accident reporting, and inspections</div>
      <div><b>Fuel Efficiency:</b> smooth acceleration, idle reduction, load management</div>
      <div><b>Post-Incident Coaching:</b> collision review and behavior correction</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="program-options reveal">
    <h2>Corporate Program Options</h2>

  <div class="tiers">
    <div class="tier">
      <h3>Standard Safety Package — <span>$250 / driver</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>1-day on-site training and evaluation</li>
        <li>Defensive driving and compliance basics</li>
        <li>Certificate of completion for each driver</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">Ideal for small fleets and logistics companies needing annual re-training.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tier premium reveal">
      <h3>Professional Fleet Program — <span>Custom Quote</span></h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Multi-day program customized for your operation</li>
        <li>On-road, yard, and classroom modules</li>
        <li>Accident review, coaching, and performance tracking</li>
        <li>Digital reports for compliance and insurance purposes</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="note">Best for mid-size and large fleets aiming to improve long-term driver safety KPIs.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  </section>

  <section class="benefits reveal">
    <h2>Benefits for Your Company</h2>
    <div class="facts">
      <div><b>Reduce Risk:</b> fewer collisions and violations mean lower insurance costs.</div>
      <div><b>Stay Compliant:</b> training meets MTO and DOT requirements for fleet operations.</div>
      <div><b>Boost Performance:</b> drivers operate more efficiently and professionally.</div>
      <div><b>Enhance Reputation:</b> safer fleets attract better contracts and customers.</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq reveal">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can you train drivers at our facility?</h3>
      <p>Yes. We can deliver training on-site at your yard or office anywhere in the GTA.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Do you offer customized corporate packages?</h3>
      <p>Absolutely. Programs are tailored to your fleet size, vehicle type, and safety requirements.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Will our drivers receive certificates?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Each participant receives a completion certificate for HR and insurance records.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can you help after a collision or violation?</h3>
      <p>Yes. We provide post-incident evaluations, one-on-one coaching, and official documentation for carrier files.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>
</Transition>
